(Rapid serial visual presentation, or RSVP, shows text one) Tj T*
(word at a time in a fixed position. Because your eyes never) Tj T*
(move, the usual cost of saccades disappears. Many readers) Tj T*
(can comfortably double their reading speed this way.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
